text: Jordan Banjo (born 31 December 1992) is a British street dancer. He is also best known as a brother of the leader of the dance troupe Diversity Ashley Banjo. ==Works== He is best known as a current member of the dance troupe Diversity. They won the third series of Britain's Got Talent. He and fellow Diversity star Perri Kiely co-host the KISS weekday breakfast show. He is currently a guest of the ITV celebrity competition I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here!. Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:British dancers
title: Jordan Banjo
